---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Strategy — Bidwell Capital" description="We chase cashflow. Income-producing, tax-advantaged real assets.">
  <section class="hero-sm">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label fade-up fade-up-1">Strategy</span>
      <h1 class="fade-up fade-up-2">We chase cashflow</h1>
      <p class="fade-up fade-up-3">Bidwell Capital is focused on income-producing, tax-advantaged real assets. We have found that the assets that generate the best cashflow and tax benefits also tend to appreciate — but nothing is guaranteed.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="thesis-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Investment Thesis</span>
          <h2>Cashflow first. Always.</h2>
          <p>Most investors are overexposed to equities and underexposed to real assets. Index funds are excellent tools, but they offer no tax advantages, no income diversification, and no downside protection beyond broad market diversification.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">We look for assets that put money in your pocket every month. Tax benefits are a close second — and we have found that the assets that check both of those boxes also tend to appreciate over time. But we never count on appreciation. Cashflow pays the bills.</p>
          <p class="disclaimer" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">All investments involve risk, including the possible loss of principal. Past performance is not indicative of future results. Nothing on this website constitutes a guarantee of any return.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            <h3>Income First</h3>
            <p>Every strategy we run is designed to generate regular cashflow. Monthly distributions, contractual interest, rental income — we want assets that pay you to own them.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            <h3>Tax Efficiency</h3>
            <p>We actively seek tax-advantaged structures. Cost segregation, bonus depreciation, intangible drilling costs, and preferred return structures all work in the investor's favor.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Operator Alignment</h3>
            <p>We invest our own capital alongside our investors. We are operators, not salespeople — our underwriting and deal flow come from direct experience in real estate and energy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">What We Invest In</span>
      <h2>Three asset classes, one philosophy</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">We operate across commercial real estate credit, multifamily real estate, and energy. Each one is selected because it produces income, offers tax advantages, and is backed by a tangible asset.</p>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <span class="badge">Commercial Real Estate Credit</span>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 1rem;">Private Commercial Credit Fund</h3>
          <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Preferred equity and mezzanine debt positions across commercial real estate — multifamily, industrial, medical office, and more. Structured with forced sale and take-over rights for downside protection.</p>
          <a href="/track-record" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.875rem;">View PCCF Dashboard &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="badge">Multifamily Real Estate</span>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 1rem;">Multifamily Fund</h3>
          <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Direct ownership and management of multifamily properties. Tax-advantaged through cost segregation and bonus depreciation. 35+ units owned and managed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="badge">Energy</span>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 1rem;">Oil &amp; Gas Working Interests</h3>
          <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Working interest positions in oil and gas. Significant tax deductions through intangible drilling costs, with exposure to a commodity backed by real-world demand.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">About the Founder</span>
      <h2>Adam Penn</h2>
      <p>Software engineer turned real estate operator and fund manager. Adam started his first rental in 2017 while working in tech, eventually building a portfolio of 35+ units, a property management company, and launching Bidwell Capital. He is based in Northern California and co-hosts the <a href="https://www.wealthindependencepod.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--accent);">Wealth Independence Podcast</a>.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">Adam's approach is rooted in engineering: systematic underwriting, data-driven decision making, and a focus on building repeatable, scalable systems.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-sm {
    padding: 5rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .hero-sm h1 {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .hero-sm p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .thesis-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .thesis-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
